author: Rick Cantu
title: State-ranked and unbeaten, Lake Travis, Westlake set to clash
text:
Westlake can end seven years of misery by playing 48 minutes of winning football Friday night against Lake Travis.
Surviving the first quarter, though, will have to be the Chaparrals’ first order of business against the Cavaliers.
